    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "I'm sitting here looking at my hands and they don't even feel like mine anymore. Everything is just... slowing down. It's not even painful, really, it's just so quiet and lonely. Sometimes I feel like I'm just a ghost waiting for my body to realize I'm already gone.",
